song.title: Zeta
song.info:
Done for the sample pack compo. It was done seriously, as i enjoy tracking with one sample, but i of course knew it would end up in bottom bunch, not in top, so it's not a serious effort compowise, if you know what i'm talking about :D Title is Zeta because i didn't have any tune beginning with "Z".
Oh yeah, the "transition" in 1:49 or so is not an accident but done intentionally :)
